   with a sentence + link. This is a maintenance pass, not a sprint.

⬜ SVG diagrams for hard concepts
   ASCII art is in versioning.md and node-recovery.md.
   The convergence model and the 4-layer truth model still lack visual diagrams.
   These would convert the most mentally dense pages into something scannable.
   Requires: someone to produce SVGs or use a diagram tool.

⬜ Getting Started still assumes the release tarball exists
   Option A references a GitHub release that doesn't exist yet.
   The note is there, but it's still the first option shown.
   Self-heals when v0.1.0 is tagged and released.
